{"tid":1835904,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：有病唔洗醫，檢疫侵犯人權","createTime":"2020-01-23T04:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T04:39:02.000Z","uid":38139,"like":155,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fb3d375ff2c490b1f42f039e2b4a8396e45cdc","tid":1835904,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至於沙士、禽流感這些病，也是一樣。你不理會它，它只是惡性的流感而已，一年半載就會被人體適應，而其實他們一直存在與某些人類之中而相安無事</span></span>。我講出這些真相，一定被人攻擊，注定一世無運行，窮過鬼。<br />\n我在2003年沙士的時候，我也勸告政府毋須理會，但結果呢？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港發現了病毒和治療法，也死人最多。很多人升官發財，機場也將作狀的檢疫恆久化，不斷侵擾人權。</span></span>之後，我被逼離開政府，這只是其中一個原因&mdash;&mdash;我阻止政府部門膨脹，我阻止人升官發財。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJMDhvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJMDhvF.png&h=20c78760&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MemcmXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMemcmXk.png&h=d2651fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgoKc31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgoKc31.png&h=872a5e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過兩日改撚哂口風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你老母咪同我講咩醫學陰謀論，唔好以為我唔識字<br />\n唔明d 人點解要吹捧呢條撚屌"},{"pid":"af26798a64e942c9b2343618cb1fe83b385f0670","tid":1835904,"uid":108337,"like":51,"dislike":4,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"陳雲死全家"},{"pid":"7c3af90a1d0d0830ce839ae503dfcdfaf0546e7a","tid":1835904,"uid":165234,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":